A betting game company, ILOT NG has empowered football lovers in Nigeria to eradicate poverty in the country. The Company’s industrial manager, Abass olaitan made this known to newsmen on Monday in Lagos. Abass explained that ILOT NG believes many Nigerians have various football teams they are in love with doing well in their leagues. The Manager further explained that football lovers are empowered through their beliefs and luck as the rate of unemployment is on the increase.   Child prodigy Onazi wins Awosika’s scrabble tournament     African Championships: Nigeria grabs three medals on final…     Dare lauds FCT SWAN on Easter, Sallah gifts   While emphasising on registering on the firm’s website, Abass commended the National Lottery Regulatory Commission for providing the most reliable and the best betting in Nigeria. “ILOT NG empowers football lovers through their beliefs and luck. “Why we are embarking on this is because there are lots of people who are jobless, and have nothing to take care of themselves and their families due to the current situation of the country. “ILOT NG believes many Nigerians have their various football teams they are in love with and those teams are doing well in their leagues and they could express their predictability through sport bet like football, tennis, basketball, rugby, Lottery games, quick 3, super 5/90 and the likes,” he said.